make

public static final void make(java.io.InputStream in,
                              java.lang.String outFilename,
                              boolean log)
                       throws java.io.IOException
Reads a word list from in and writes a set of dictionary files out which are prefixed with outFilename.

Parameters:
in - The word list to read in.
outFilename - The path and filename prefix for the new on-disk dictionary.
log - If true, we'll write to stdout as we create load the words from in.
Throws:
java.io.IOException
